==Setup==
Setup for SPM 12 (r6470). In order to run SPM on legion, you need to have the Matlab R2015a (v 8.5) module loaded and the SPM module. To use SPM 8 instead, load a different SPM module. <br />

<code>module load matlab/full/r2015a/8.5</code><br /><code>module load spm/12/r6470/matlab.r2015a</code><br /><br />These add SPM to your MATLABPATH. They are the MATLAB toolbox version and not standalone versions.

When constructing job scripts, remember to load the modules in the job script (or your .bashrc).







